messages.message:
This might be a bad time to ask since the investigation for <#C051K9C8LTT|> and the dogfood deployment issues are ongoing

but are we still sticking to this requirement?

we merged a lot of PRs yesterday, and we’ll continue to merge a lot of PRs today, so i’m concerned that none of those changes will make it into the last successful dogfood deployment
The dogfood deployment issue from yesterday is resolved and we are going to monitor it on Monday before code cut, so yes the requirement will stay.
